project_descr: UN Joint Programme on Gender Equality

outputs.output_descr:
United Nations - Government of Viet Nam Joint Programme on Gender Equality MDGF 1694. There are 3 joint outcomes and each joint outcome has 3 outputs as follows:
Output 1.1: Capacity assessed of the SMAs, line ministries, National Assembly, Communist Party, mass
organizations including the Vietnam Women’s Union and concerned agencies at the local level
to implement, monitor, evaluate and report on the two laws.
Output 1.2: Relevant plans of action developed for the SMAs, line ministries, National Assembly and
Communist Party at the central and local levels to implement, evaluate, monitor
